parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PTU can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or shift erratically, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The "Service Four Wheel Drive" message appears on the dashboard
the vehicle stalls or shifts erratically
and the vehicle makes abnormal noises such as clunking or whistling sounds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission and clutch can cause the vehicle to stall, shift erratically, or lose power, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or hesitates to shift
the transmission slips or makes abnormal noises
the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
and the vehicle makes abnormal noises such as clicking or clunking sounds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auto stop/start system can cause the vehicle to stall or struggle to restart, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: the auto stop/start warning light comes on
the vehicle shuts off while driving

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electronic emergency brake can cause the vehicle to suddenly stop or lose control, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The electronic emergency brake engages on its own

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the BCM can cause various electrical systems to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
The failure of the climate control system can cause the windows to fog up, reducing visibility and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: the air conditioning does not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the shifter can cause the vehicle to become stuck in gear, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
The failure of the UConnect system can cause the entertainment system to freeze, which can be a distraction for the driver and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: the SOS call system locks up
the entertainment system does not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TPMS can cause the driver to be unaware of a tire pressure loss, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: the front driver-side tire does not register on the warning screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering rack gear can cause the vehicle to lose steering control, leading to accidents or near-miss situations, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly jerks or turns to one side
the steering wheel becomes firm or difficult to turn
the power steering lock warning light is illuminated
and the steering wheel has a "knotty" or stuck feeling.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electronic Steering Power Transfer Unit Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic steering power transfer unit can cause the vehicle to lose steering control, leading to accidents or near-miss situations, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly jerks or turns to one side
the steering wheel becomes firm or difficult to turn
the power steering lock warning light is illuminated
and the vehicle vibrates or shakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering control module can cause the vehicle to lose steering control, leading to accidents or near-miss situations, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The power steering lock warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes firm or difficult to turn
and the vehicle vibrates or shakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive engine oil consumption can lead to premature engine wear, increased emissions, and potentially cause engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Fuel system leaks or fires can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to the risk of explosion or fire.
Engine stalling or loss of power can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to the loss of vehicle control.
Low oil pressure warnings can indicate engine damage or failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
